text.textblock: Notice is hereby given of a change in the March 1, 1994, meeting of the National Institute on Deafness and Other Communication Disorders Special Emphasis Panel, which was published in the

This Special Emphasis Panel was to have convened at 8 a.m. on March 1, 1994, at the Chevy Chase Holiday Inn, but has been changed to 8 a.m., March 11, 1994, at the Bethesda Marriott, 5151 Pooks Hills Road, Bethesda MD.
The meeting will be closed to the public.
(Catalog of Federal Domestic Assistance Program No. 93.173 Biological Research Related to Deafness and Other Communicative Disorders)
